{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01TD58sDqYmqUgELQ8q7aVTH","type":"tool_result","content":"# Harness Cost Report\n\nTotal API-equivalent cost: $808.12\nTotal API calls: 5892\nAverage cost per story: $3.80 (158 stories)\n\n## Cost by Token Type\n\n| Type | Tokens | Rate | Cost | % |\n|------|--------|------|------|---|\n| Cache reads | 316,245,048 | $1.50/MTok | $474.37 | 59% |\n| Cache writes | 11,053,759 | $18.75/MTok | $207.26 | 26% |\n| Output | 1,683,791 | $75/MTok | $126.28 | 16% |\n| Input | 14,152 | $15/MTok | $0.21 | 0% |\n\n## Cost by Phase\n\n| Phase | Calls | Cost | % |\n|-------|-------|------|---|\n| verify | 3447 | $432.49 | 53.5% |\n| orchestrator | 820 | $178.21 | 22.1% |\n| retro | 677 | $92.79 | 11.5% |\n| code-review | 333 | $37.98 | 4.7% |\n| create-story | 344 | $36.58 | 4.5% |\n| dev-story | 271 | $30.07 | 3.7% |\n\n## Cost by Tool\n\n| Tool | Calls | Cost | % |\n|------|-------|------|---|\n| Bash | 2217 | $272.77 | 33.8% |\n| Read | 1230 | $168.66 | 20.9% |\n| Edit | 900 | $116.39 | 14.4% |\n| Agent | 556 | $72.81 | 9.0% |\n| Skill | 196 | $67.74 | 8.4% |\n| Grep | 389 | $44.69 | 5.5% |\n| Write | 154 | $27.49 | 3.4% |\n| Glob | 107 | $18.82 | 2.3% |\n| TodoWrite | 111 | $15.24 | 1.9% |\n| ToolSearch | 28 | $3.10 | 0.4% |\n\n## Top 10 Most Expensive Stories\n\n| Story | Calls | Cost | % |\n|-------|-------|------|---|\n| unknown | 1042 | $207.11 | 25.6% |\n| 16-5-rewrite-harness-run-verification-dispatch | 488 | $58.48 | 7.2% |\n| 1-1-foo | 198 | $24.35 | 3.0% |\n| 14-5-stack-aware-verify-dockerfile | 190 | $23.63 | 2.9% |\n| 14-4-observability-backend-choice | 192 | $22.13 | 2.7% |\n| 8-9-semgrep-rules-rust-observability | 121 | $17.10 | 2.1% |\n| 8-2-expand-state-types-for-rust | 84 | $12.67 | 1.6% |\n| 9-5-multi-stack-docs-remaining-consumers | 84 | $11.07 | 1.4% |\n| 11-2-sprint-status-yaml-derived-view | 74 | $10.80 | 1.3% |\n| 11-1-unified-sprintstate-schema-versioning | 75 | $10.27 | 1.3% |\n[OK] Report saved to /Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/cost-report.md","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01GMoJgYFpogbpKCSAFkyAUw","session_id":"a0f2adac-1266-43b8-bf07-8e8d43548e26","uuid":"5ed7536d-a99f-4464-9d50-ff834bc28dde","timestamp":"2026-03-28T07:27:15.124Z"}
